  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/786805017391c9c9f2f5db30448943ed.poster.avif?t=1750782632\" width=612 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/786805017391c9c9f2f5db30448943ed.webm?t=1750782632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/786805017391c9c9f2f5db30448943ed.mp4?t=1750782632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>DJ CLICKER DISCORD COMMUNITY</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/aa3c0c7f2f822c0e24f2847c49b06f93.avif?t=1750782632\" width=616 height=280 /></span><br><br><strong>DJ Clicker - World Tour</strong> is a game about you and what you're gonna do with your life. <br><br>You can travel the world and become a famous star DJ, but you need to have the energy for it. Hit the lights and set up your loops until you're pumped up enough to take it to the stage. Collect tracks and fame to play the biggest venues.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/a32291d79e9164be986aa63d84fd6dbe.poster.avif?t=1750782632\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/a32291d79e9164be986aa63d84fd6dbe.webm?t=1750782632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/a32291d79e9164be986aa63d84fd6dbe.mp4?t=1750782632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/960cbf20d2a53609974ce23a45cadfa5.avif?t=1750782632\" width=616 height=280 /></span><br><br>The game is all about electronic music composed by artists from all over the world. There will be 72 tracks to unlock as well as different vinyls, record covers, locations and residences. It also includes 2 brand new tracks from famed games music composer Chris Huelsbeck (Star Wars Rogue Squadron, Turrican, Giana Sisters). <br><br>If you love music and want a game with no fighting, then DJ Clicker is for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/49b8476efe625e9bd4d4c353015a891c.avif?t=1750782632\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/1091f1ecbad9f29997c119838b004a3f.poster.avif?t=1750782632\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/1091f1ecbad9f29997c119838b004a3f.webm?t=1750782632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/1091f1ecbad9f29997c119838b004a3f.mp4?t=1750782632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Here is a small preview of some of the records you can collect:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/12acc29d71e68ada2dfdfa7c8babf4ed.avif?t=1750782632\" width=616 height=480 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/786805017391c9c9f2f5db30448943ed.poster.avif?t=1750782632\" width=612 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/786805017391c9c9f2f5db30448943ed.webm?t=1750782632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/786805017391c9c9f2f5db30448943ed.mp4?t=1750782632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>DJ CLICKER DISCORD COMMUNITY</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/aa3c0c7f2f822c0e24f2847c49b06f93.avif?t=1750782632\" width=616 height=280 /></span><br><br><strong>DJ Clicker - World Tour</strong> is a game about you and what you're gonna do with your life. <br><br>You can travel the world and become a famous star DJ, but you need to have the energy for it. Hit the lights and set up your loops until you're pumped up enough to take it to the stage. Collect tracks and fame to play the biggest venues.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/a32291d79e9164be986aa63d84fd6dbe.poster.avif?t=1750782632\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/a32291d79e9164be986aa63d84fd6dbe.webm?t=1750782632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/a32291d79e9164be986aa63d84fd6dbe.mp4?t=1750782632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/960cbf20d2a53609974ce23a45cadfa5.avif?t=1750782632\" width=616 height=280 /></span><br><br>The game is all about electronic music composed by artists from all over the world. There will be 72 tracks to unlock as well as different vinyls, record covers, locations and residences. It also includes 2 brand new tracks from famed games music composer Chris Huelsbeck (Star Wars Rogue Squadron, Turrican, Giana Sisters). <br><br>If you love music and want a game with no fighting, then DJ Clicker is for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/49b8476efe625e9bd4d4c353015a891c.avif?t=1750782632\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/1091f1ecbad9f29997c119838b004a3f.poster.avif?t=1750782632\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/1091f1ecbad9f29997c119838b004a3f.webm?t=1750782632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/1091f1ecbad9f29997c119838b004a3f.mp4?t=1750782632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Here is a small preview of some of the records you can collect:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571200/extras/12acc29d71e68ada2dfdfa7c8babf4ed.avif?t=1750782632\" width=616 height=480 /></span>",
